'''伯克利加利福尼亞大學'''（{{lang-en|University of California, Berkeley}}；常用[[縮寫|縮寫]]：{{lang|en|UC Berkeley或Cal}}），[[簡稱|簡稱]]'''伯克利加大'''、'''伯克利加州大學'''，又常被譯為'''加利福尼亚大学伯克利分校'''、'''加州大學柏克萊分校'''、'''伯克利大学'''，是一所位於[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[舊金山灣區|舊金山湾区]][[伯克利_(加利福尼亞州)|伯克利市]]，世界著名的[[公立|公立]][[研究型大學|研究型大學]]。伯克利加大是[[加利福尼亞大學|加利福尼亞大學]]系统的创始大学，建立於1868年，在2021年泰晤世全球聲譽排名第6名，同時在众多机构排名位列全球大学排行前十名，是世界顶尖的公立大学之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.usnews.com/best-colleges/rankings/national-universities/top-public |title=US NEWS BEST PUBLIC UNIVERSITIES |accessdate=2021-03-06 |author= |date= |publisher= |deadurl= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223062939/https://www.usnews.com/best-colleges/rankings/national-universities/top-public |archivedate=2017-02-23 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.shanghairanking.com/ARWU2020.html|title=ARWU World University Rankings 2020 {{!}} Academic Ranking of World Universities 2020 {{!}} Top 500 universities {{!}} Shanghai Ranking - 2020|accessdate=2021-03-06|work=www.shanghairanking.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180816224432/http://www.shanghairanking.com/ARWU2020.html|archive-date=2018-08-16|dead-url=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2021/world-ranking#!|title=World University Rankings|newspaper=Times Higher Education (THE)|accessdate=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902154147/https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2021/world-ranking#!|archive-date=2020-09-02|dead-url=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2020/reputation-ranking#!|title=World Reputation Rankings|newspaper=Times Higher Education (THE)|accessdate=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626213556/https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2020/reputation-ranking#!|dead-url=|archive-date=2019-06-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.usnews.com/education/best-global-universities/rankings|title=Best Global Universities Rankings (US News)|accessdate=2021-03-06|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028092904/http://www.usnews.com/education/best-global-universities/rankings|archive-date=2014-10-28|dead-url=}}</ref>。

伯克利是[[美國大學協會|美國大學協會]]的14个創始會員之一，并与[[美國能源部|美国能源部]]的三所美国国家实验室保持紧密联系，包括[[劳伦斯伯克利国家实验室|劳伦斯伯克利国家实验室]]、[[勞倫斯利福摩爾國家實驗室|勞倫斯利福摩爾國家實驗室]]以及[[洛斯阿拉莫斯国家实验室|洛斯阿拉莫斯国家实验室]]，而许多世界著名的研究机构包括[[美国国家数学科学研究所|美国国家数学科学研究所]]、[[伯克利空间科学实验室|伯克利空间科学实验室]]也都位于伯克利<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.lbl.gov/about/|title=About the Lab|date=2013-05-18|newspaper=Berkeley Lab|accessdate=2017-01-16|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118082201/http://www.lbl.gov/about/|archive-date=2017-01-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.llnl.gov/about|title=History|last=|first=|date=2013-10-09|work=|newspaper=Lawrence Livermore National Laboratory|accessdate=2017-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121110922/https://www.llnl.gov/about|archive-date=2017-01-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=About|url=http://www.lanl.gov/about/index.php|accessdate=2017-01-16|last=Energy|first=Los Alamos National Laboratory, Operated by Los Alamos National Security, LLC, for the U.S. Department of|work=www.lanl.gov|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116034601/http://www.lanl.gov/about/index.php|archive-date=2017-01-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=MSRI|url=http://www.msri.org/web/msri/about-msri/history|accessdate=2017-01-16|last=MSRI|work=www.msri.org|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220095632/http://www.msri.org/web/msri/about-msri/history|archive-date=2017-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ssl.berkeley.edu/about/visiting/|title=Visiting|date=2011-03-10|newspaper=Space Sciences Laboratory|accessdate=2017-01-16|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207102234/http://www.ssl.berkeley.edu/about/visiting/|archive-date=2017-02-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。通过与[[加州大学旧金山分校|加州大学旧金山分校]]合作，伯克利还设置有医学教学及研究项目<ref>{{Cite web|title=2018-19 Best Hospitals Honor Roll and Medical Specialties Rankings|url=https://health.usnews.com/health-care/best-hospitals/articles/best-hospitals-honor-roll-and-overview|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=US News|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016061035/https://health.usnews.com/health-care/best-hospitals/articles/best-hospitals-honor-roll-and-overview|archive-date=2019-10-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

截止2020年10月，伯克利的校友、教授及研究人员中共产生了[[各大學諾貝爾獎得主列表|110位诺贝尔奖得主]]（世界第三）、[[各大学菲尔兹奖得主列表|14位菲爾茲獎得主]]（世界第四）、[[各大学图灵奖得主列表|25位图灵奖得主]]（世界第三），其他还包括9位[[沃爾夫獎|沃爾夫獎]]得主、45位[[麥克阿瑟獎|麥克阿瑟獎]]得主<ref>{{cite web|url=http://newscenter.berkeley.edu/2010/09/28/macarthur/|title=Two young faculty members named MacArthur "genius" fellows|accessdate=2012-06-08|date=2010-09-28|last=Maclay|first=Kathleen|publisher=Newscenter.berkeley.edu|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150104181856/http://newscenter.berkeley.edu/2010/09/28/macarthur/|archive-date=2015-01-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、20位[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]得主及19位[[普利策奖|普利策奖]]得主。1930年代，[[欧内斯特·劳伦斯|欧内斯特·劳伦斯]]教授在伯克利发明了[[回旋加速器|回旋加速器]]，基于此该校以及[[劳伦斯伯克利国家实验室|勞倫斯伯克利國家實驗室]]的研究人员共發現了16種[[化學元素|化學元素]]、位居世界第一，其中第97号元素“[[鉳|鉳]]（Berkelium）”即是以伯克利來命名<ref>{{Cite web|title=Berkeley Lab History – 75 Years of World-Class Science|url=http://history.lbl.gov/|accessdate=2017-01-16|work=history.lbl.gov|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161123045700/http://history.lbl.gov/|archive-date=2016-11-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Chemical Elements Discovered at Lawrence Berkeley National Laboratory|url=http://www.lbl.gov/Science-Articles/Archive/new-elements-here.html|accessdate=2011-02-21|date=1999-06-07|publisher=Lbl.gov|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180925043226/http://www2.lbl.gov/Science-Articles/Archive/new-elements-here.html|archive-date=2018-09-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。1940年代，“[[原子弹|原子弹]]之父”[[罗伯特·奥本海默|罗伯特·奥本海默]]、“[[氢弹|氢弹]]之父”[[愛德華·泰勒|愛德華·泰勒]]均曾长期担任伯克利教授，并在此领导了[[曼哈顿计划|曼哈顿计划]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=J. Robert Oppenheimer Centennial - Exhibit|url=http://cstms.berkeley.edu/archive/oppenheimer/exhibit/|accessdate=2017-01-16|work=cstms.berkeley.edu|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204154206/http://cstms.berkeley.edu/archive/oppenheimer/exhibit/|archivedate=2013-12-04|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ssl.berkeley.edu/about/history/|title=History|date=2011-03-11|newspaper=Space Sciences Laboratory|accessdate=2017-01-16|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021050047/http://www.ssl.berkeley.edu/about/history/|archive-date=2016-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1960年代，伯克利学生发起的“[[言论自由运动|言论自由运动]]”、“反越战运动”等等在美国社会产生了深远影响，改變了几代人對政治和道德的看法<ref>{{Cite web|title=Days of Cal {{!}} Berkeley in the 60s|url=http://bancroft.berkeley.edu/CalHistory/60s.html|accessdate=2017-01-16|work=bancroft.berkeley.edu|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130114053209/http://bancroft.berkeley.edu/CalHistory/60s.html|archive-date=2013-01-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Berkeley FSM {{!}} Free Speech Movement 50th Anniversary|url=http://fsm.berkeley.edu/|accessdate=2017-01-16|work=fsm.berkeley.edu|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808121625/http://fsm.berkeley.edu/|archive-date=2017-08-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。21世纪，伯克利已成为最具[[创业|创业]]精神的大学之一，其校友在世界各地创建了大量公司，包括[[英特尔|英特尔]]、[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]、[[特斯拉汽车|特斯拉汽车]]、[[摩根士丹利|摩根士丹利]]、[[软银集团|软银集团]]、[[美国国际集团|美国国际集团]]、[[爛番茄|烂番茄]]、[[动视暴雪|动视暴雪]]等等<ref>{{Cite web|title=The list of top schools for producing tech entrepreneurs shows how clubby Silicon Valley is|url=https://qz.com/1066880/the-list-of-top-schools-for-producing-tech-entrepreneurs-shows-how-clubby-silicon-valley-really-is/|accessdate=2019-07-30|last=Hao|first=Karen|work=Quartz|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190718194906/https://qz.com/1066880/the-list-of-top-schools-for-producing-tech-entrepreneurs-shows-how-clubby-silicon-valley-really-is/|archive-date=2019-07-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=In startup sweepstakes, it’s Cal vs. Stanford|url=https://news.berkeley.edu/story_jump/in-startup-sweepstakes-its-cal-vs-stanford/|accessdate=2019-07-30|date=2016-09-09|last=S|first=Robert|work=Berkeley News|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730002803/https://news.berkeley.edu/story_jump/in-startup-sweepstakes-its-cal-vs-stanford/|archive-date=2019-07-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=UC Berkeley third-largest producer of entrepreneurs, report says|url=https://www.dailycal.org/2013/08/18/uc-berkeley-third-largest-producer-of-entrepreneurs-report-says/|accessdate=2019-07-30|date=2013-08-19|last=Staff|first=Simon Greenhill {{!}}|work=The Daily Californian|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730010740/https://www.dailycal.org/2013/08/18/uc-berkeley-third-largest-producer-of-entrepreneurs-report-says/|archive-date=2019-07-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=University Entrepreneurship Report - $12.6 Billion Invested in 559 Deals|url=https://www.cbinsights.com/research/university-entrepreneurship-report/|accessdate=2019-07-30|date=2012-10-29|work=CB Insights Research|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190718200658/https://www.cbinsights.com/research/university-entrepreneurship-report/|archive-date=2019-07-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

